Class StaffVM

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.cafesystem.StaffVM
  • public class StaffVM
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a view model for the Staff class (fName,lName,email,isActive,isDeleted,createdDate). This class exposes certain Staff properties.
